race.description: Tint Tech And Auto Maiden Handicap
race.comment: CHEVALLUM (2) debuts and has switched from a NZ yard. He's been a while coming to the races but won a recent Doomben trial and looks to have good ability. Finds a winnable assignment. MISS HIGHFALUTIN (14) has switched from the Gollan yard on a 47-day return. He's been racing in stronger maidens and might be ready to recapture his early form. Will be tough to beat if he does. MAFIOSA (10) resumed improved beaten 1.8L at Toowoomba and will be better for it. He positions forward and should get every chance at an each-way quote. YES DONALD YES (3) debuts for the Bruce yard. has a wide gate but has trialled strongly and has to be considered.
